# Structure

## backend/

- main.py: FastAPI routes + static hosting
- serve.py: launcher (supports --config)
- app_config.py: loads config.yaml and prepares inputs/outputs dirs
- doc_parser.py: docx -> text
- decompose_service.py: decomposition logic + prompt
- schedule_service.py: scheduling logic + prompt
- estimate_service.py: estimation logic + prompt
- llm_client.py: OpenAI-compatible client + mock fallback
- storage.py: JSON read/write utilities

## frontend/

- public/index.html: entry (CDN Vue/AntD/dayjs)
- src/main.js: bootstraps SFC loader and registers components
- src/App.vue: header + workspace layout
- src/components/: shared components
- src/views/: decompose/schedule/estimate views

## scripts/

- start.sh: start backend (also serves frontend)
- start_backend.sh: same (CONFIG/PORT/HOST env supported)
- start_frontend.sh: same (frontend is served by backend)
